Fieldwork Maps: Cambodia precipitation


Note: The precipitation data used to make these maps is from TerraClimate monthly normals (1981-2010)

Monthly precipitation maps

TerraClimate normals (mean monthly 1981-2010)


Total annual precipitation map


Seasonality index (SI) of mean monthly precipitation

Note: SI of 0 means that precipitation is uniformly distributed throughout the year. SI of 1 means that all of the annual precipitation occurs in a single month.


Seasonal concentration (SC) of mean monthly precipitation

Note: Seasonal concentration represents the time in which precipitation is most concentrated. The values represent and angle (e.g.0 is Jan 1st, and 180 is end of June,).
